{"id": "art-588", "label": "Art. 588", "title": "Art. 588: Anularea şi revocarea liberării condiţionate", "slug": "art-588", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_942846353\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1092\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_942846353\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 588:\nAnularea &#351;i revocarea liber&#259;rii condi&#355;ionate </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_109637524\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1091\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_109637524\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Asupra anul&#259;rii liber&#259;rii condi&#355;ionate\nprev&#259;zute la art. 105 alin. (1) din </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>Codul\npenal</span><span style='color:black'> se pronun&#355;&#259;, din oficiu sau la\nsesizarea procurorului sau a consilierului de proba&#355;iune, instan&#355;a\ncare judec&#259; ori a judecat în prim&#259; instan&#355;&#259;\ninfrac&#355;iunea care atrage anularea.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1415570924\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1090\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1415570924\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Instan&#355;a prev&#259;zut&#259; la alin. (1) se\npronun&#355;&#259; &#351;i asupra revoc&#259;rii liber&#259;rii\ncondi&#355;ionate, în situa&#355;ia prev&#259;zut&#259; la art. 104 alin. (2)\ndin Codul penal .</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_464635907\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1089\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_464635907\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)Instan&#355;a prev&#259;zut&#259; la art. 587 alin. (1)\nse pronun&#355;&#259; &#351;i asupra revoc&#259;rii liber&#259;rii\ncondi&#355;ionate, în situa&#355;ia prev&#259;zut&#259; la art. 104 alin. (1)\ndin </span><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>Codul penal</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>, la sesizarea serviciului de proba&#355;iune, precum\n&#351;i în cazul când instan&#355;a care l-a judecat pe condamnat pentru o\nalt&#259; infrac&#355;iune nu s-a pronun&#355;at în aceast&#259;\nprivin&#355;&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1262278559\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1088\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1262278559\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Instan&#355;a în fa&#355;a c&#259;reia hot&#259;rârea a\nr&#259;mas definitiv&#259; este obligat&#259; s&#259; comunice locului de\nde&#355;inere &#351;i serviciului de proba&#355;iune, atunci când este cazul, o\ncopie de pe dispozitivul prin care s-a dispus revocarea liber&#259;rii\ncondi&#355;ionate.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;\nmargin-bottom:0in;margin-left:0in;text-align:center'><span style='mso-no-proof:\nyes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape id=\"Imagine_x0020_986245398\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1087\"\n type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;\n mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"Codul%20de%20Procedura%20Penala%20.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_986245398\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>SEC&#354;IUNEA\n2:Amânarea execut&#259;rii pedepsei închisorii sau a deten&#355;iunii pe\nvia&#355;&#259;</span></b></p>"}